  248:				;========================
  249:				; AI MOVE - Priority based strategy:
  250:				; 1. Win  : complete own line of 2
  251:				; 2. Block: stop X from winning
  252:				; 3. Fork : create 2 ways to win
  253:				; 4. Block fork: stop X creating 2 ways
  254:				; 5. Center
  255:				; 6. Opposite corner of X
  256:				; 7. Any corner
  257:				; 8. Any edge
  258:				;========================
  259:	  0188			AI_MOVE:
  260:				        ; --- Priority 1: Win immediately ---
  261:	  0188	12 01 F8	        LCALL FIND_WIN_O
  262:	  018B	40 65		        JC AI_DONE
  263:
  264:				        ; --- Priority 2: Block X from winning ---
  265:	  018D	12 02 24	        LCALL FIND_BLOCK_X
  266:	  0190	40 60		        JC AI_DONE
  267:

ASEM-51 V1.3                                         Copyright (c) 2002 by W.W. Heinz                                         PAGE 6



 Line  I  Addr  Code            Source

